ters\n- **Completed:** F1-F6 (ClickHouse client, migrations, dev setup, identity resolution, POST /api/events, POST /api/events/batch)\n\n### 8. MEMORY.md\nDoes not exist at project root.\n\n---\n\n## Key Takeaways for Implementation\n\n1. **Testing pattern:** Use `vi.hoisted()` for mock setup, mock at module level before imports, and create hoisted error classes for instanceof checks\n2. **Route pattern:** Parse JSON, handle errors with appropriate HTTP status codes, return JSON responses\n3. **Type exports:** Identity.ts provides all core types and functions; QueryEventsOptions already supports pagination params (before cursor, limit)\n4. **Error handling:** IdentityConflictError has status property; other errors are generic Error instances\n5. **CLI commands:** `npm test`, `npm run lint`, `npm run typecheck`, `npm run build`"}],"totalDurationMs":34254,"totalTokens":87188,"totalToolUseCount":13,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":124,"cache_read_input_tokens":85681,"output_tokens":1378,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":124},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":5,"output_tokens":1378,"cache_read_input_tokens":85681,"cache_creation_input_tokens":124,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":124,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"toolStats":{"readCount":8,"searchCount":3,"bashCount":2,"editFileCount":0,"linesAdded":0,"linesRemoved":0,"otherToolCount":0}}}
